          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Legal directories matter more than general ones</h4>
              <p>Avvo, FindLaw, Justia, and Martindale-Hubbell citations carry more ranking authority for attorney searches than Yelp or generic directories.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS ROW -->
  <section>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">10<span class="accent"></span></div><div class="stat-label">Tools tested for law firm SEO</div></div>
