      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#6 · FROM $130/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Semrush — Best for legal keyword research and competitive analysis</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For large law firms or legal marketing agencies with a dedicated SEO professional and budget to match.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Semrush has the largest keyword database available. Keyword difficulty and CPC data helps prioritize which legal practice areas offer the best organic ROI. Competitive analysis shows competitor organic keywords and traffic sources. Listing management available at additional cost. The $130/month baseline and steep learning curve make it overkill for solo practitioners or firms in low-competition markets.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
